{"arkId":"cl010099915","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099915","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XVI (1774-1792) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1640 - 1660 (bo\u00eetier et cadran) et 1785 - 1800 (mouvement)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1640,"endYear":1660,"imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1785,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Henou Embden, Charles","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8317","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Fond du bo\u00eetier orn\u00e9 d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne repr\u00e9sentant Le Jugement de P\u00e2ris : celui-ci d\u00e9signe Aphrodite comme la plus belle des trois d\u00e9esses, au-dessus d\u0027elle, un amour tenant une couronne et une palme. Int\u00e9rieur du fond contre-\u00e9maill\u00e9 d\u0027un paysage o\u00f9 apparaissent un joueur de fl\u00fbte et une jeune femme gardant des moutons. Couvercle figurant L\u0027Enl\u00e8vement d\u0027H\u00e9l\u00e8ne : au centre se trouve P\u00e2ris la conduisant par le bras, accompagn\u00e9e de ses suivants, vers un navire. Int\u00e9rieur du couvercle peint d\u0027un paysage bois\u00e9 o\u00f9 deux personnages conversent. Pourtour d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de six m\u00e9daillons ovales contenant des paysages marins. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains, d\u00e9cor\u00e9 au centre d\u0027un paysage avec des ruines, o\u00f9 au premier plan une berg\u00e8re se laisse enlacer par un galant. Mouvement muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre ; balancier dot\u00e9 d\u0027un ressort-spiral. Coq circulaire \u00e0 un pied, de style anglais, grav\u00e9 et reperc\u00e9 de rinceaux o\u00f9 se trouvent deux oiseaux.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Charles \/ Henou Embden","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"9,2","displayDimension":"9,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6,8","displayDimension":"6,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,2","displayDimension":"2,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6,5","displayDimension":"6,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 652 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Olivier, Marie-Julie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"Olivier, Jules-Ren\u00e9","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"24\/01\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"05\/02\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"04\/08\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis XIV (1643-1715)"},{"value":"Louis XVI (1774-1792)"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres du Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 1, [Collection Olivier], Paris, RMN, 1984","bibliographyDate":"1984","bibliographyDetail":"n\u00b0 51","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000099915\/0000743837_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000099915\/0000743837_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 1983 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean\/Schormans","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000099915\/0000182153_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000099915\/0000182153_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 1983 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Photographe inconnu","type":"","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000099915\/0000182154_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000099915\/0000182154_OG.JPG","copy